*DESCRIPTION_START
Part human, part machine these rigid custodians of the law have gone
through an intensive training program that makes them the elite of the elite.
Bristling with weaponry and bearing the city seal of Fayd they are sworn
to uphold the law, and will do so with any means at their disposal.
*DESCRIPTION_END
