Standing before you is the latest advancement in law enforcement.
Employing the lastest in the cybernetic fields, this is one officer you
do not want to mess with. You notice a large cylnderical device mounted
to its shoulder. A titanium badge of the lawkeepers is mounted to one of
its armor plates.
